examples.en: Negotiations were at a complete standstill.
examples.ru: Переговоры не сдвигались с мёртвой точки.

examples.en: The accident brought traffic to a standstill.
Work on the project has crawled to a standstill.
...the irrelevance of the comment brought conversation to a standstill...
He had almost run himself to a standstill.
examples.ru: Он набегался так, что не мог сдвинуться с места.
